ions</code></p> <pre><code>{\n  \"amount\": 1500,\n  \"date\": \"2025-03-25T12:00:00\",\n  \"description\": \"\u041f\u043e\u043a\u0443\u043f\u043a\u0430 \u043d\u043e\u0443\u0442\u0431\u0443\u043a\u0430\",\n  \"type\": \"expense\",\n  \"category_id\": 2,\n  \"weight\": 1.5\n}\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"lr_1/task/#_11","title":"\u041f\u043e\u043b\u0443\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u0432\u0441\u0435\u0445 \u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0437\u0430\u043a\u0446\u0438\u0439 \u043f\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044f","text":"<p>GET <code>/transactions</code></p>"},{"location":"lr_1/task/#_12","title":"\u0410\u043d\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0442\u0438\u043a\u0430","text":""},{"location":"lr_1/task/#_13","title":"\u041f\u043e\u043b\u0443\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043e\u0442\u0447\u0435\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u043f\u043e \u043a\u0430\u0442\u0435\u0433\u043e\u0440\u0438\u044f\u043c \u0440\u0430\u0441\u0445\u043e\u0434\u043e\u0432","text":"<p>GET <code>/analytics/expenses</code> \u041e\u0442\u0432\u0435\u0442:</p> <pre><code>[\n  {\n    \"category\": \"\u041f\u0440\u043e\u0434\u0443\u043a\u0442\u044b\",\n    \"total_spent\": 5000\n  },\n  {\n    \"category\": \"\u0420\u0430\u0437\u0432\u043b\u0435\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f\",\n    \"total_spent\": 2000\n  }\n]\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"lr_1/task/#pydantic-","title":"Pydantic-\u0441\u0445\u0435\u043c\u044b","text":""},{"location":"lr_1/task/#schemasbudgetpy","title":"<code>schemas/budget.py</code>","text":"<pre><code>from pydantic import BaseModel\n\nclass BudgetBase(BaseModel):\n    limit: float\n    category_id: int\n\nclass BudgetCreate(BudgetBase):\n    pass\n\nclass BudgetResponse(BudgetBase):\n    id: int\n    user_id: int\n    category_name: str\n\n    class Config:\n        from_attributes = True\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"lr_1/task/#schemasuserpy","title":"<code>schemas/user.py</code>","text":"<pre><code>from pydantic import BaseModel, EmailStr\n\nclass UserCreate(BaseModel):\n    email: EmailStr\n    password: str\n\nclass UserResponse(BaseModel):\n    id: int\n    email: EmailStr\n\n    class Config:\n        from_attributes = True\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"lr_1/task/#alembic","title":"\u041c\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 (Alembic)","text":""},{"location":"lr_1/task/#_14","title":"\u0421\u043e\u0437\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043c\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438","text":"<pre><code>alembic revision --autogenerate -m \"\u0414\u043e\u0431\u0430\u0432\u043b\u0435\u043d\u044b \u0442\u0430\u0431\u043b\u0438\u0446\u044b\"\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"lr_1/task/#_15","title":"\u041f\u0440\u0438\u043c\u0435\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043c\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0439","text":"<pre><code>alembic upgrade head\n</code></pre>"}]}